{"tid":1577413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"9月過左一半，又係時候同大家溫定書啦","createTime":"2019-09-17T16:27:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T00:21:02.000Z","uid":219681,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7c9157c2c393a465cc7958f3336fdc30ac560cac","tid":1577413,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:27:04.000Z","msg":"反佔中活動已經過左百日，五大訴求，政府仍然無一回應<br />\n與此同時，<span style=\"color: red;\">黑警濫補，傷害，殺害，迫害</span>我兄弟姐妹過千人，希望大家唔好忘記，當你地「生活」緊既時候，有好多好多受左傷同被捕既手足正響度受苦。若然大家放軟手腳，放棄自己，就係對敵人仁慈，對手足殘忍。<br />\n以下附上一堆支線同戰略分析，希望帶俾各位思考空間，調整，再升級各活動方向同力度。<br />\n<br />\n1) <span style=\"color: gold;\">草木皆兵，莫因事小而不為</span><br />\n保護手足，需要好大既勇氣，我知道唔可能個個都會好似「岳」巴咁，能夠做到捨己救人。但兄弟有難，不得不救。我建議由即日起，舉行<span style=\"color: orange;\">全民Full Gear</span> 或者<span style=\"color: orange;\">全民黑色口罩</span>活動。響可能既情況下，大家都以勇武衣著表達對前線尊敬，同時將Black Block 升級，用「和理非」之身保護「真。勇武」既手足。當然，呢個做法係有風險既，而佢既風險就係「太少人參加」。如果動員力不足，「和理非」手足係增加被捕或者被「福建幫」打傷既風險。但同樣，呢個做法亦可以大大保護手足，特別係防止「有Gear」即「被捕」既情況。由於優劣參半，呢個位置開放討論。<br />\n<br />\n2) <span style=\"color: gold;\">冷處理 / 無視林鄭設立既對話平台</span><br />\n好多兄弟可能等緊機會，準備到現場示威或者發洩。但係我想講，呢個做法非常錯。其實林鄭設「社區對話會」，同我地設連儂牆既道理係「一模一樣」。佢最怕係冇人睇，冇人報，冇人破壞。如果大家到場示威，就同藍蛆撕牆一樣，會吸引目光。如果你去破壞佢，就會被「冠以」示威者破壞「對話平台」既污名。其實今日政府都表左態話「預左有人破壞」，既然係咁，我地就要令佢失預算。呢場明顯係一場「公關」Show，其實「冷眼旁觀」就已經係最好既回應方式。當然，大家可以照報名，但唔需要出現。與此同時，大家可以考慮響同一時間搞「萬人集思會」，將傳媒既目光「帶走」。<br />\n<br />\n3) <span style=\"color: gold;\">香港民主人權法案 只為開啟下一章 非終局</span><br />\n好多風向都講過「香港民主人權法案」要「通過」其實唔難，但「執行」先係最難既事。美國係唔可能唔「支持」我地爭取「民主」，但呢個法案係咪真係咁大影響力 ? 佢既影響係個體 ? 定係整個「中共」體制 ? 其實佢好大機會只係令小部份「利益集團」既得益受損。但之後呢 ? 香港庫房大把錢，其實一個「明日大魚」既已經可能令佢地回血從生。我必須重申，我並唔係唔支持大家將無助投放響呢個法案上，但大家都必須要有心理準備，成功與否都唔係All or nothing。我地仍然有好多好多主線目標要做，唔應該過份依賴某一主線成就，去到下一章唔代表爆左機，呢個只係助攻，希望大家明白。<br />\n<br />\n4) <span style=\"color: gold;\">台灣局勢 至為重要</span><br />\n「柯」，「郭 」相繼退選，小英表面上勝算高左，但「中共」統戰部已經即刻派出「呂」出黎界票。可以講，「中共」策略一直跟住台灣「民調」改變。「韓」由「必勝」到而家「落後」，可以話係香港人幫左台灣一把。但事實上台灣實體經濟真係唔太好，台灣人能否堅持落去，唔為錢低頭，仍然係一個問題，所謂「唇亡齒寒」，好多兄弟會視台灣為「退路」或者民主既「最後一片樂土」，既然係咁，大家必須Connect，必須互相幫手。其實好多台灣人都好支持香港，希望大家唔好忘記呢個一水之隔既盟友，打算去旅行既各位，亦可以考慮下台灣，去玩既時候，亦不妨感染下台灣既朋友，我地必須要用行動支持佢地，令佢地都無後顧之憂。<br />\n<br />\n5) <span style=\"color: gold;\">藍蛆文宣雖可笑，但不得不防</span><br />\n大家或多或少都睇過唔同既藍蛆文宣，當中少不了「抹黑」「作新聞」「剪接」<br />\n曾經，大家都當係笑話，弱智先會信，但其實呢D新聞既「受眾」從來都唔係大家，而家欠缺J圖既「藍蛆」。呢D假文宣，係要鼓吹藍蛆傷害手足，因為佢地以為自己做緊「正義」既事。<br />\n阻人打飛機，絕對係一個好既選擇，我建議大家「有組織」「有系統」地統領「網軍」，唔係Report 呢D Page 咁簡單，而係互推互Like控制風聲，與其Report完再等人做野，不如大大力洗乾淨佢，洗到佢地Admin 懷疑人生。<br />\n<br />\n6) <span style=\"color: gold;\">防分化，防大台</span><br />\n講到口臭都要再提，呢場運動，「內訌」絕對係事旦一方「玩能完」既條件<br />\n再講一次，所謂既「不分化」，所講既係一個「不論立場」「互相尊重」既概念。<br />\n策略重點，係因時制宜，勇武同和理，決一不可。<br />\n成個活動，目標相同，大家各自努力，依賴既係「心領神會」同「互相信任」。<br />\n「以牙還牙」係必須，但打一個藍蛆，同救一班兄弟都可能被捕，點解唔將勇氣放響後者?<br />\n如果你有方法，有能力，令「黑警」同「福建幫」都為己所用，咁先係真正贏。<br />\n<br />\n7) <span style=\"color: gold;\">認清敵人，集中火力</span><br />\n前文提要:<br />\n香港人，點解你地仲未知道邊個先係大家既「真正敵人」?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1519660\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1519660</a><br />\n<br />\n十月就到，我相信我地偉大既「內地同胞」又會按耐不住好奇心，黎香港參觀<br />\n有見及此，我地必須要把握機會，輸出革命，文宣組必須集中火力響「高鐵站」「機場」「車站」「遊客區」做宣傳，建議手足可以預先分「主題」同「地點」做文宣<br />\n<br />\n「你在牆內的日子」<br />\n「你所不知道的集政權」<br />\n「親，民主是個好東西」<br />\n「牆內那麼好，為什麼要走出來」<br />\n<br />\n大家互相保護，齊上齊落<br />\n希望大家響 唱歌，大叫，遊行 既同時，無忘初衷<br />\n對我黎講，只有手足生者平平安安，死者沉冤得雪，五大訴求終如願，<br />\n香港成為最民主，和平，進步之地，先係「真正勝利」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">各位加油，願正義必勝</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YiuZOCQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYiuZOCQ.jpg&h=625fb340&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7569303630b191cb8fdce7e4f39e08f4934594e","tid":1577413,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:27:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自推 1/10"},{"pid":"fa7bf42afb96c5a76b6e87faa0661fc9d5bb9c7f","tid":1577413,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:27:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自推 2/10"},{"pid":"37993779fe5e79fb61f801935733a596a477dd56","tid":1577413,"uid":266617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:28:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1cae184189ae7a7ec990b1df438b4a40ff4494c7","tid":1577413,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:28:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自推 3/10"},{"pid":"ac3ae4abf7b4135ed0b11743c237f707f59a9e84","tid":1577413,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:28:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自推 4/10"},{"pid":"c15a217fd8924127c632165e6e6ec8409942d560","tid":1577413,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:28:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自推 5/10"},{"pid":"99ff63648d2849d6a5812465416d6046d8d7da0a","tid":1577413,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:29:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自推 6/10"},{"pid":"79e39705dddc929a4f0b82af3b4d220f00e94c55","tid":1577413,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:29:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自推 7/10"},{"pid":"4243c76b08f5ad16cfd9be19b3ac84bea6195308","tid":1577413,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:29:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自推 8/10"},{"pid":"96fe2893d7379ac6da89639b7dbaa13a913f6e6f","tid":1577413,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:30:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自推 9/10"},{"pid":"7cfc7a33162d8ab8f12f9281255cf51fcb626310","tid":1577413,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:30:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自推 10/10"},{"pid":"3852ed968f007044d31b7304947bc8ec7479fdf6","tid":1577413,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:31:03.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73235299928009d23793d678f790731dd6ac618a","tid":1577413,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:31:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登仔去曬邊阿"},{"pid":"03a56e4777d777199a735cc45890715c230967c4","tid":1577413,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:32:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wxU7c6R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwxU7c6R.jpg&h=ef9a83a7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CMLFx6T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCMLFx6T.jpg&h=f08a3ff2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n黑社會還腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83dd448466ca4558bfc0133ebb0ee5c72c7a3dd3","tid":1577413,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:33:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d607f64dca0228433cb595922f2b911208cbd63","tid":1577413,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:36:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb413eb3b8efe6f17f85ad3411d199b549d00950","tid":1577413,"uid":101824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:38:30.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命。"},{"pid":"2276f52035124cb46b43bb6b621eb09ac0d1d3bf","tid":1577413,"uid":143382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:40:22.000Z","msg":"温故而知新 <br />\n可以為師焉"},{"pid":"6915227a465bd10126993c3ab789b8f4d907101a","tid":1577413,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:44:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 文宣兄弟姊妹響度嘛"},{"pid":"70aa93ceaf1fb6debaed03c61efe8efb19f5fd2d","tid":1577413,"uid":133903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T16:52:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"40892b7ab5ab4f4eefadf019ba7aea525e8d7a99","tid":1577413,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T17:03:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都知我好長氣⋯⋯⋯"},{"pid":"3cfaa0edc3a91dc5a36e8c60c647613c1dfc86e3","tid":1577413,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T17:04:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bace6b233eeaa8fe678e69af858cdea20d1ba86","tid":1577413,"uid":219681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T17:18:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e56fd5466f142b46f9eb285eafd15c459057e7","tid":1577413,